.TH "of_usb_update_otg_caps" 9 "of_usb_update_otg_caps" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
of_usb_update_otg_caps \- to update usb otg capabilities according to the passed properties in DT.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" of_usb_update_otg_caps
.BI "(struct device_node *np "  ","
.BI "struct usb_otg_caps *otg_caps "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "np" 12
Pointer to the given device_node
.IP "otg_caps" 12
Pointer to the target usb_otg_caps to be set
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
The function updates the otg capabilities
